---
---

<section id="what-i-do" class="wid-section">
  <h2 class="visually-hidden">What I do</h2>

  <div class="wid-intro fade-up" data-delay="80">
    <p class="wid-statement">
      I own the technical decisions from first use case to production: what to build, what to buy, what it costs to run, and who operates it after launch. Strategy when you need it, engineering when you need that too.
    </p>
    <p class="wid-sub">
      Twenty years building systems that fail in public if they fail at all. That's the standard I bring to AI in production.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="wid-beats">

    <div class="beat fade-up" data-delay="160">
      <!-- Selection matrix: identify the one signal from the noise -->
      <svg class="beat-icon" viewBox="0 0 56 56" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
        <rect x="0.5" y="0.5"  width="15" height="15" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.75"/>
        <rect x="20.5" y="0.5" width="15" height="15" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.75"/>
        <rect x="40.5" y="0.5" width="15" height="15" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.75"/>
        <rect x="0.5" y="20.5"  width="15" height="15" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.75"/>
        <rect x="20.5" y="20.5" width="15" height="15" stroke-width="1.5" style="stroke:var(--cobalt)"/>
        <rect x="40.5" y="20.5" width="15" height="15" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.75"/>
        <rect x="0.5" y="40.5"  width="15" height="15" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.75"/>
        <rect x="20.5" y="40.5" width="15" height="15" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.75"/>
        <rect x="40.5" y="40.5" width="15" height="15" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.75"/>
        <circle cx="28" cy="28" r="2" style="fill:var(--cobalt)"/>
      </svg>
      <h3 class="beat-title">Find the right use case</h3>
      <p class="beat-body">Not every problem needs AI, and not every AI needs an agent. I help you pick the few use cases that pay for themselves, and rule out the ones that won't.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="beat fade-up" data-delay="240">
      <!-- Hub & spoke: central agent orchestrating connected components -->
      <svg class="beat-icon" viewBox="0 0 56 56" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
        <rect x="0.5"  y="0.5"  width="11" height="11" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.75"/>
        <rect x="44.5" y="0.5"  width="11" height="11" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.75"/>
        <rect x="0.5"  y="44.5" width="11" height="11" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.75"/>
        <rect x="44.5" y="44.5" width="11" height="11" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.75"/>
        <line x1="11.5" y1="11.5" x2="23.4" y2="23.4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.75"/>
        <line x1="44.5" y1="11.5" x2="32.6" y2="23.4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.75"/>
        <line x1="11.5" y1="44.5" x2="23.4" y2="32.6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.75"/>
        <line x1="44.5" y1="44.5" x2="32.6" y2="32.6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.75"/>
        <circle cx="28" cy="28" r="6.5" stroke-width="1.5" style="stroke:var(--cobalt)"/>
      </svg>
      <h3 class="beat-title">Build the system</h3>
      <p class="beat-body">Agents, RAG, automation, and the systems around them. Built for reliability, observability, and a cost you can predict. Hosted, or on open models you control.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="beat fade-up" data-delay="320">
      <!-- Nested boundary: presence inside the codebase, not advising from outside -->
      <svg class="beat-icon" viewBox="0 0 56 56" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
        <rect x="0.5"  y="0.5"  width="55" height="55" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.75" stroke-dasharray="3 2"/>
        <rect x="13.5" y="13.5" width="29" height="29" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"/>
        <circle cx="28" cy="28" r="5"   stroke-width="1.5" style="stroke:var(--cobalt)"/>
        <circle cx="28" cy="28" r="1.5" style="fill:var(--cobalt)"/>
      </svg>
      <h3 class="beat-title">Build and operate, not just advise</h3>
      <p class="beat-body">Code, architecture reviews, production debugging, and staying on to keep it running. I work in your repository, not from the outside.</p>
    </div>

  </div>

</section>

<style>
  .wid-section {
    background: var(--white, oklch(99% 0 0));
    padding: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 7rem) clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
    border-bottom: 1px dotted var(--rule, oklch(87% 0.005 260));
  }

  /* ── Full-width intro ── */
  .wid-intro {

    padding-top: clamp(2.5rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
    margin-bottom: clamp(3rem, 5vw, 5rem);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 4rem);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .wid-statement {
    font-size: var(--text-lead-size, clamp(1rem, 1.5vw, 1.125rem));
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: var(--text-lead-lh, 1.7);
    color: var(--ink, oklch(10% 0.012 258));
    max-width: 52ch;
  }

  .wid-sub {
    font-size: var(--text-body-size, 1rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: var(--text-body-lh, 1.875);
    color: var(--dim, oklch(28% 0.010 258));
    max-width: 52ch;
  }

  .wid-sub strong {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink, oklch(10% 0.012 258));
  }

  /* ── Three beats - horizontal row ── */
  .wid-beats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    border-top: 1px dotted var(--rule, oklch(87% 0.005 260));
  }

  .beat {
    padding: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 3rem) clamp(1.5rem, 2.5vw, 2.5rem);
    border-right: 1px dotted var(--rule, oklch(87% 0.005 260));
  }
  .beat:first-child { padding-left: 0; }
  .beat:last-child  { border-right: none; padding-right: 0; }

  .beat-icon {
    display: block;
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
    color: oklch(74% 0.004 260);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .beat-title {
    font-size: clamp(1.15rem, 2vw, 1.6rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--ink, oklch(10% 0.012 258));
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .beat-body {
    font-size: var(--text-body-size, 1rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: var(--text-body-lh, 1.875);
    color: var(--dim, oklch(28% 0.010 258));
    max-width: 36ch;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1000px) {
    .wid-intro { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .wid-beats {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .beat {
      border-right: none;
      border-bottom: 1px dotted var(--rule, oklch(87% 0.005 260));
      padding: 2rem 0;
    }
    .beat:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  }
</style>
